# 📁 EDMS: Alignsys Web Client

> A fully functional **Electronic Document Management System (EDMS)** with a modern front-end interface for accessing, managing, and collaborating on documents.

---

## 🌟 Key Features

- 🔍 Full document search and filtering
- 📂 Browse vaults, views, and document metadata
- 📝 Metadata editing and version control
- 🧩 Workflow handling and assignment
- 🗃️ Create, update, and delete objects (Documents, Assignments, etc.)
- 👥 Support for users and user groups
- 📤 Upload documents and manage files
- 💬 Commenting and activity logs per document
- 📱 Fully responsive front-end built with **React** + **MUI** (Material UI)

---

