## 🚀 Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|-------|------------|
| Frontend | React, Material UI, Axios, React-PDF, React Router |
| Backend | M-Files REST API (via proxy or direct) |
| Deployment | Docker / Vite / Nginx |

---

## 🛠️ Installation & Setup

### 1. Clone the Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/msyoki/edms-alignsys-web-client.git
cd edms-alignsys-web-client
```

### 2. Install Dependencies

```bash
npm install
```

### 3. Configure Environment

Create a `.env` file in the project root:

```env
VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://your-mfiles-server/REST
VITE_API_USERNAME=your_username
VITE_API_PASSWORD=your_password
```

### 4. Run the Development Server

```bash
npm run dev
```

Then open your browser at:

```
http://localhost:5173
```

### 5. Build for Production

```bash
npm run build
```

---

## 🐳 Docker Deployment (Optional)

```bash
docker build -t edms-alignsys .
docker run -p 80:80 edms-alignsys
```

Or with Docker Compose:

```bash
docker-compose up --build
```

