## 📁 Project Structure

```
edms-alignsys-web-client/
├── public/
├── screenshots/
├── src/
│   ├── api/           # Axios API calls & M-Files REST integration
│   ├── components/    # Reusable UI components
│   ├── pages/         # Route-level page components
│   ├── hooks/         # Custom React hooks
│   ├── context/       # Auth and app-level context providers
│   └── utils/         # Helper functions
├── .env.example
├── Dockerfile
├── vite.config.js
└── package.json
```

---

## 🔌 API Integration

This client connects to the **M-Files REST API**. Ensure your M-Files server is running and accessible, then set the base URL in your `.env` file.

| Endpoint Area | Description |
|---------------|-------------|
| `/session` | Authentication & vault selection |
| `/objects` | Document CRUD operations |
| `/files` | File upload and download |
| `/workflows` | Workflow state management |
| `/comments` | Document comments and activity logs |

---

## 💡 Notes

> ⚠️ Before pushing to GitHub, make sure to:

- Never commit `.env` — add it to `.gitignore`
- Use `.env.example` to document required variables without exposing secrets
- Avoid committing large files from `screenshots/` unless lightweight

### Recommended `.gitignore` entries

```gitignore
.env
node_modules/
dist/
.DS_Store
```

